metadata.name: RHYTHM OF COLORS
metadata.description:
RHYTHM OF COLORS

This photo won a gold medal with "Aydin efes" in the homeland themed photography competition held in Hipa in 2019.

Zeybek is a local folk dance.Zeybek represents a brave man who protects the people.
It can be played by one person or several people.

Game figures vary according to the player's emotions and skills. For this reason, in single zeybeks, there are differences in the gait, collapse and turns of those who play the same game. Tabs, knee kicks, walks in the game symbolize zeybek's self-confidence, honesty, bravery and challenge to the environment.


Efe and Zeybek outfits are truly magnificent and embroidered with extraordinary delicacy.


Artis: Seckin Yenici
 Edition: 1/1
Date: 2015
File: jpeg 300 dpi
Location: Kusadasi - Aydin / Türkiye
Image Size: 5400x 3600
